<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP8">
<l>pariya ṉākivan tavavu ṇaṉuṭal kīṇṭa vamarark</l>
<l>kariya vātippi rāṉaraṅ kattama laṉmukattuk</l>
<l>kariya vākip puṭaiparantu miḷirntu cevvari yōṭi nīṇṭavap</l>
<l>periya vāyakaṇ kaḷeṉṉaip pētaimai ceytaṉavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those great eyes—dark, broad, gleaming, red-streaked,</l>
<l>long, on the face of the flawless [Lord] of Raṅgam,</l>
<l>the primordial Lord, hard [to approach] for the immortals,</l>
<l rend="indent">who tore apart the body of the bulky Asura who turned up—</l>
<l>have driven me insane.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
